<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#TSJN-01-03-0601-fn-0001-ptr" id="TSJN-01-03-0601-fn-0001">1</a><p>The passage marked by an asterisk, for which there is no corresponding asterisk in the text, may have been intended as a postscript pertaining to the foregoing paragraph.</p></div>
